Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.53,0:00:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.65,0:00:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.38,0:00:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 補給部搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.83,0:00:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是12mm法蘭管件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.64,0:00:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱要的是10mm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.88,0:00:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<黑耀>上能用 但銀色殲滅者用不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.88,0:00:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 也不能怪他們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.43,0:00:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10mm很少有人用的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.25,0:00:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.17,0:01:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算想提意見 隊長和鈴城小姐也都不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.08,0:01:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為啥這會兒還被叫去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.43,0:01:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.67,0:01:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更重要的是法蘭管件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.89,0:01:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,試作機型就這點麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.86,0:01:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,缺乏可維護性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.10,0:01:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也常聽人這樣說 真差這麼多嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.06,0:01:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以說中看不中用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.38,0:01:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是高端新型機
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.25,0:01:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有量產機完全沒法比的大量專用配件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.73,0:01:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不能用其他曳戰者的配件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.89,0:01:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.60,0:01:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟外觀就跟其他機體不同啊 這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.38,0:01:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用時留點神
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.99,0:01:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然關鍵時刻掉鏈子就沒你的戲唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.94,0:01:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我{\rsymbol}…{\r}我會注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.50,0:01:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.04,0:01:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶 你看它的腳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.69,0:01:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用了散熱和減震的雙重構造
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.41,0:01:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是很優雅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.29,0:01:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.28,0:01:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼傻話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.65,0:01:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰場上需要的 可不是婦孺的優雅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.76,0:01:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是爺們的蠻勇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.15,0:02:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 班長又性別歧視
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.77,0:02:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.88,0:02:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦 有空動嘴不如多動手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說 法蘭管件怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.47,0:02:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是老婆 不能離婚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.78,0:02:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不合適的只能強扭它合適
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由於閃擊戰失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.61,0:03:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因戈爾米亞戰力被迫分為南北兩部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿蘭達斯軍隨一時後撤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.59,0:03:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻趁因戈爾米亞行軍減緩之際 調整了態勢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.14,0:04:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正伺機反攻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.39,0:04:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各地雖小規模戰鬥不斷 卻沒有大規模進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣過了些時日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.72,0:04:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,獨立第八部隊轉戰各地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如今在威修佩地區 稍事休養
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)\pos(980,575)}不在之終
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.27,0:04:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.11,0:04:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.15,0:04:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 天堂 天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.22,0:05:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在澡堂說{\rsymbol2}「{\r}天堂天堂{\rsymbol2}」{\r}的 現實中還是第一次見到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.04,0:05:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是奶奶帶大的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.90,0:05:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 還好威修佩有溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.05,0:05:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皮膚好滑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.32,0:05:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滑溜溜的皮膚就近在咫尺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託也為我這只能看見爺們屁股的人著想一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓開 在哪 在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.83,0:05:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.17,0:05:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.77,0:05:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺行啊 你小子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.58,0:05:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來啊來啊 抓我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.61,0:05:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男浴池吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是哪個混蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.09,0:05:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別跑 別跑 別跑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.31,0:05:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對面不可能看得到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,堂堂偶像怎麼能為這點事害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋名小姐 你是偶像?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.84,0:05:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坯子而已 還是落選的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.75,0:05:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好意外
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.97,0:05:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶 都試唱過什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:05:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.95,0:05:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨便唱兩句
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要買的 就這些了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.98,0:06:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喲 這不是尾久井家的小伙子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔 好久不見了 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.93,0:06:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 嘛 還真是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔 小伙子 最近還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位是{\rsymbol}…{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同隊的越川
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙他照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.62,0:06:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你小子參軍之後 一次都沒回來過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.84,0:06:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾過來露個臉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等有時間的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.53,0:06:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 好稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼突然回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.41,0:06:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是威修佩人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.44,0:06:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啥都沒有的落後小鎮而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不碰上熟人都難
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.63,0:07:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小時候在這鎮子 我每天都想離開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在看還成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是{\rsymbol}…{\r}篠井老太婆?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.86,0:07:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒斷氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有那麼容易死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你居然沒被槍子兒打得稀巴爛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.15,0:07:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.84,0:07:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臭老太婆都沒斷氣 我怎麼可能死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.31,0:07:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,窗簾 拉開了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.79,0:07:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.53,0:07:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好多灰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.89,0:07:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒人住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.31,0:07:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸媽早就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.90,0:07:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我偶爾回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.05,0:08:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.70,0:08:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 開始加壓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.63,0:08:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖說不算完美 但應該能撐到下次補給
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進展如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔 快了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後就看你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.59,0:08:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,設備識別和磨合你來搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.09,0:08:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶 為什麼這全塗黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這些是第二整備
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.03,0:08:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二整備
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.53,0:08:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現場能完成的叫第一整備
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其餘的 要送到工廠才能搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為是試作品 裡面滿是柯貝爾尼斯工業的企業機密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.31,0:08:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能做第一整備的地方很有限
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.69,0:09:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家忙整備時你去泡溫泉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.83,0:09:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泡得好舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想泡溫泉就快幹活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.53,0:09:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,溫泉溫泉 趕緊搞定這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.77,0:09:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞 快點動手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,溫泉溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.44,0:09:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是第八部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.19,0:09:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因戈爾米亞穿過塔斯卡衝這邊來了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.22,0:09:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狀況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.11,0:09:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還在確認
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.28,0:09:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦 隊長不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.67,0:09:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔斯卡陷落看來是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.71,0:10:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如今左文字隊長和鈴城曹長不在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.75,0:10:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指揮權落在谷田軍曹身上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谷田軍曹吃魚中毒正在蹲廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為生吃了河裡釣的魚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.16,0:10:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.58,0:10:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然谷田軍曹身體不適{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.49,0:10:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.57,0:10:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道要曳戰者機師來指揮?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.35,0:10:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦喲 我可不幹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.33,0:10:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來 輪到尾久井或轡田啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.36,0:10:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.23,0:10:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.03,0:10:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.34,0:10:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找熟悉本地地理的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.41,0:10:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,熟悉地理{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.97,0:10:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 趕緊搬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.44,0:11:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之 請盡量拖延時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.21,0:11:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.95,0:11:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱的傢伙可沒多少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.92,0:11:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寺井 申請援軍了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.78,0:11:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,申請了 但總部也正頭疼如何應對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.39,0:11:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵方部隊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.53,0:11:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通過塔斯卡的是一個師團
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不久後 至少會有三個大隊向這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,優先讓平民去避難
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.31,0:11:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完成後 開始反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.60,0:11:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,班長做好炸橋準備
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.49,0:11:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行了 你們幾個無論如何 也要把銀色殲滅者準備好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人過一陣才會抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.67,0:11:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必驚慌 完全來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.09,0:11:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請冷靜轉移
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還想死在這鎮上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你死時的樣子 可沒人想看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.87,0:11:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鎮子我來想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是席加 敵人接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.57,0:12:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已確認12台曳戰者 這就發圖像
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鎮民避難如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒結束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人進軍比預想快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去 再沒多久威修佩就會進入射程
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.15,0:12:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-10配件給我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真安靜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.29,0:12:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是暴風雨前的那玩意?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.90,0:12:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我受不了沉默啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過會兒你就覺得安靜是福了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大夥兒 千萬別挨敵人槍子兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.27,0:13:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏這會兒食物中毒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別停 徑直去橋那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.88,0:13:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的 冷靜轉移
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是席加
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.51,0:14:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵方曳戰者開始入侵城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.29,0:14:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.10,0:14:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位 守住位置
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 然後去向麵包店那個轉角
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麵包店?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.73,0:14:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:14:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:14:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,扳手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.28,0:14:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊還在用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:14:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.99,0:15:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒見到敵人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說尾久井 指揮拜託給點力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那邊右轉{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃{\rsymbol}…{\r}不對 左轉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.07,0:15:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底哪邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.05,0:15:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊是山並 現在敵人到哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.47,0:15:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人{\rsymbol}…{\r}敵人到這個{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.56,0:15:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.49,0:15:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消滅一台曳戰者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 沒人掩護嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中彈了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別一下都來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.34,0:15:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在你是指揮官
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.64,0:15:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左文字隊長平時都在做這種事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.05,0:15:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不得不承認被壓制了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.01,0:15:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 到處是敵人 該往哪打
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.66,0:15:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我 鎮民避難馬上完成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狀況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點 馬上要起霧了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個季節 會有很濃的河霧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:15:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起霧{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:16:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是一流的援軍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.72,0:16:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霧哪能說{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.17,0:16:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說起就起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.89,0:16:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒 這是搞啥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起霧倒是不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.51,0:16:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可這下 不好打了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一個是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.87,0:16:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我 鎮民避難完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鎮民全員過橋了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.25,0:16:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全員 開始反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.88,0:16:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在怎麼反擊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.18,0:16:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵軍已經太深入了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.88,0:16:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再說這霧啥都看不見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.47,0:16:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尾久井 銀色殲滅者還沒動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒修好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.98,0:16:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到極限了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太懸了啊喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:16:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.06,0:17:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人後續部隊 確認20台曳戰者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全員 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.47,0:17:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轉輪旋轉 目測穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.79,0:17:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,油壓穩定了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.45,0:17:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,輔助系統的SP值 進不到正常範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.84,0:17:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀色殲滅者還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.32,0:17:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.15,0:17:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.82,0:17:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀色殲滅者 裝置 喚醒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.65,0:18:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,系統啟動流程 運行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.71,0:18:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轉寫 吉米·哈茲福特 接入
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.76,0:18:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時宗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.14,0:18:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.93,0:18:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快 跑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.67,0:18:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.76,0:18:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.72,0:18:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尾久井 開車
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.67,0:18:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 時宗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.80,0:18:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.99,0:18:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.16,0:18:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,班長 這邊好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.54,0:19:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.77,0:19:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.69,0:19:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時宗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.30,0:19:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.37,0:19:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.35,0:19:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.65,0:19:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時宗 過橋後立刻動手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.03,0:19:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.65,0:19:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.23,0:20:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時宗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 時宗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶 說話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.27,0:20:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是{\rsymbol}…{\r}時宗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.88,0:20:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.46,0:20:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.57,0:20:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.32,0:20:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.52,0:21:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.97,0:21:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.18,0:21:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喲 來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.47,0:22:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進來吧
